{"tid":999513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Margot Robbie,Ewan McGregor主演《猛禽小隊》釋出前導預告","createTime":"2019-01-28T18:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T19:12:03.000Z","uid":212399,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4d70339d8d5416980e97d386967d45437a53a0","tid":999513,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"2016 年由大衛艾耶（David Ayer）執導的《自殺突擊隊》（Suicide Squad）雖然沒有獲得太好的評價，但票房成績依舊不俗，此外由瑪格羅比（Margot Robbie）飾演的「小丑女」哈莉奎恩也獲得相當大的迴響與人氣，而她領銜的電影《猛禽小隊》（暫譯，Birds of Prey (And the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)&nbsp;）全新前導預告也釋出，看來剪了頭髮的哈莉瘋癲迷人依舊！<br />\n《猛禽小隊》已經選定由中國女導演閻羽茜（Cathy Yan）執導，卡司包括瑪格羅比（Margot Robbie）飾演「小丑女」哈莉奎恩、瑪麗伊莉莎白溫斯蒂（Mary Elizabeth Winstead）飾演女獵手（Huntress）、喬妮斯莫雷特貝爾（Jurnee Smollett-Bell）飾演黑金絲雀（Black Canary）、蘿西佩雷茲（Rosie Perez）飾演警探蕾妮蒙托亞（Renee Montoya）以及伊旺麥奎格（Ewan McGregor）飾演「黑面具」，預計 2020 年 2 月上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JrQTDDbti1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJrQTDDbti1Y&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=93731225\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JrQTDDbti1Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Fnews%2F16306&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=17fa2fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16306</a>"},{"pid":"3788525e16a09b758896205fea836d0d18509632","tid":999513,"uid":64374,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc8eccdaa7634434a9aa4e64f262eccf91d6cdfd","tid":999513,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://st3.depositphotos.com/1814084/15283/i/1600/depositphotos_152836716-stock-photo-mary-elizabeth-winstead.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fst3.depositphotos.com%2F1814084%2F1